WEBVTT

00:00:25.490 --> 00:00:27.090 line:80%
What are you thinking about?

00:00:27.440 --> 00:00:28.440 line:80%
Nothing.

00:00:29.280 --> 00:00:31.630 line:80%
Why do I smell something burning?

00:00:33.950 --> 00:00:35.040 line:80%
My dish!

00:00:48.690 --> 00:00:49.970 line:80%
Did something happen?

00:01:04.730 --> 00:01:07.330 line:80%
Qianqian wants to invite you
to be her husband.

00:01:08.150 --> 00:01:09.030 line:80%
What?

00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:12.839 line:80%
She sees a good catch
and now she wants to snatch him away, huh?

00:01:12.839 --> 00:01:14.720 line:80%
No, she means to "borrow" him.

00:01:15.390 --> 00:01:17.360 line:80%
To drive away a customer
who's been harassing her.

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:18.760 line:80%
That won't work, either.

00:01:19.480 --> 00:01:21.110 line:80%
Dear, why are you pulling me?

00:01:21.170 --> 00:01:22.500 line:80%
If a woman wanted to borrow you from me,

00:01:22.500 --> 00:01:23.780 line:80%
would you be okay with it?

00:01:23.780 --> 00:01:26.640 line:80%
Well, if she were gentle,
I guess I wouldn't mind.

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:28.870 line:80%
Say that again! I dare you!

00:01:28.870 --> 00:01:30.510 line:80%
What kind of reward did she offer

00:01:30.510 --> 00:01:32.480 line:80%
that you'd sell me out just for
a few taels of silver?

00:01:32.480 --> 00:01:34.970 line:80%
How could I possibly sell you out
for just a few taels?

00:01:34.970 --> 00:01:35.950 line:80%
Yeah, exactly.

00:01:35.950 --> 00:01:37.880 line:80%
A few taels do sound a bit too cheap.

00:01:38.190 --> 00:01:39.309 line:80%
Thirty taels.

00:01:40.230 --> 00:01:41.490 line:80%
-What?
-Thirty taels?

00:01:45.510 --> 00:01:48.510 line:80%
Well, Changyu means well, after all.

00:01:48.870 --> 00:01:51.140 line:80%
Yan Zheng, why don't you just help out?

00:01:51.309 --> 00:01:53.040 line:80%
Think of it as doing a good deed.

00:01:53.279 --> 00:01:54.010 line:80%
Hey, wait...

00:01:54.230 --> 00:01:55.540 line:80%
What? Why "hey, wait?"

00:01:55.559 --> 00:01:57.000 line:80%
If you could sell for even 3 or 5 taels,

00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:57.920 line:80%
I'd agree immediately.

00:01:57.920 --> 00:01:58.480 line:80%
You...

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:00.560 line:80%
Changning.

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:02.340 line:80%
Let's go. Let's ignore them.

00:02:03.150 --> 00:02:05.430 line:80%
Turns out I'm worth even less than a pig.

00:02:05.510 --> 00:02:07.640 line:80%
And how much do you think you're worth?

00:02:08.040 --> 00:02:09.710 line:80%
Why don't you ask someone else?

00:02:09.710 --> 00:02:12.160 line:80%
Like that... Lord Li or whatever.

00:02:12.710 --> 00:02:14.420 line:80%
Well, he's not in Lin'an.

00:02:18.580 --> 00:02:20.510 line:80%
Even if he were, I wouldn't ask him.

00:02:21.430 --> 00:02:23.060 line:80%
I've got my own husband—

00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:24.670 line:80%
why go to an outsider?

00:02:30.430 --> 00:02:32.040 line:80%
Just help Qianqian out.

00:02:32.270 --> 00:02:33.330 line:80%
It's just for 1 day.

00:02:33.710 --> 00:02:34.950 line:80%
If her Yixiang Restaurant goes under,

00:02:34.950 --> 00:02:36.810 line:80%
our business will suffer as well.

00:02:38.110 --> 00:02:39.480 line:80%
That rice merchant surnamed Qi

00:02:39.480 --> 00:02:41.040 line:80%
clings to her like a stubborn bandage.

00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:42.920 line:80%
He's just impossible to get rid of.

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:44.640 line:80%
Harmless, but irritating.

00:02:45.990 --> 00:02:47.720 line:80%
The rice merchant surnamed Qi?

00:02:49.290 --> 00:02:51.640 line:80%
Who has he been associating with lately?

00:02:51.670 --> 00:02:55.070 line:80%
It's said to be a rice merchant
from the Capital, surnamed Qi.

00:02:58.060 --> 00:02:58.970 line:80%
Just for 1 day?

00:02:59.040 --> 00:02:59.880 line:80%
Just for 1 day.

00:04:26.780 --> 00:04:32.250 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:04:32.330 --> 00:04:34.930 line:80%
[Episode 13]

00:04:35.020 --> 00:04:37.540 line:80%
[Welcome guests from far and wide]

00:04:46.670 --> 00:04:47.670 line:80%
This way, please.

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:48.430 line:80%
Zheng.

00:04:49.750 --> 00:04:51.800 line:80%
In this outfit, let alone
a restaurant manager—

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:53.660 line:80%
you could even pass for a marquis.

00:04:53.990 --> 00:04:55.870 line:80%
Not bad. This way, please.

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:00.920 line:80%
I'm counting on you today.

00:05:02.950 --> 00:05:03.800 line:80%
Rest assured.

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:05.070 line:80%
Changyu said

00:05:05.400 --> 00:05:07.260 line:80%
you're her best friend in Lin'an.

00:05:07.890 --> 00:05:09.190 line:80%
If she wants to help you,

00:05:09.190 --> 00:05:10.920 line:80%
I'll do it without hesitation.

00:05:12.370 --> 00:05:13.010 line:80%
This way.

00:05:14.270 --> 00:05:17.090 line:80%
[Heaven-class]

00:05:18.570 --> 00:05:19.540 line:80%
Mr. Qi.

00:05:23.910 --> 00:05:26.350 line:80%
Manager Yu, are you feeling better?

00:05:28.170 --> 00:05:31.010 line:80%
Mr. Qi, this is my husband, Yan Zheng.

00:05:51.170 --> 00:05:53.540 line:80%
He's been away on business recently.

00:05:53.540 --> 00:05:54.900 line:80%
He just returned to Lin'an today,

00:05:54.900 --> 00:05:56.100 line:80%
and I brought him here specifically

00:05:56.100 --> 00:05:59.050 line:80%
to thank you for supporting
our humble restaurant's business.

00:05:59.050 --> 00:05:59.930 line:80%
Mr. Qi.

00:06:01.010 --> 00:06:02.210 line:80%
Pleasure to meet you.

00:06:03.540 --> 00:06:05.340 line:80%
So you're Manager Yu's husband.

00:06:05.980 --> 00:06:06.640 line:80%
Naturally.

00:06:20.540 --> 00:06:23.050 line:80%
Yan Zheng, have a good chat with Mr. Qi.

00:06:23.050 --> 00:06:24.980 line:80%
I'll go prepare some food and wine.

00:06:31.010 --> 00:06:31.850 line:80%
Mr. Qi.

00:06:32.860 --> 00:06:33.459 line:80%
Please.

00:06:41.810 --> 00:06:43.350 line:80%
When Master throws his cup as a signal,

00:06:43.350 --> 00:06:45.150 line:80%
that's our cue to tie that guy up.

00:06:48.980 --> 00:06:51.540 line:80%
I heard you came from the Capital, Mr. Qi.

00:06:52.170 --> 00:06:54.690 line:80%
I wonder why you've come to
our tiny Lin'an Town

00:06:54.690 --> 00:06:55.930 line:80%
for grain business?

00:06:59.540 --> 00:07:01.980 line:80%
Mr. Yan, you're not a local here either.

00:07:02.420 --> 00:07:05.460 line:80%
So why are you running a restaurant
here in Lin'an?

00:07:11.050 --> 00:07:12.690 line:80%
My wife may not
have attended to things properly.

00:07:12.690 --> 00:07:14.220 line:80%
Please bear with us, Mr. Qi.

00:07:14.930 --> 00:07:16.530 line:80%
Next time there's business,

00:07:16.660 --> 00:07:18.190 line:80%
please come straight to me.

00:07:20.860 --> 00:07:24.050 line:80%
It's just I wonder how big a deal
you can handle, Mr. Yan.

00:07:27.700 --> 00:07:28.660 line:80%
For example...

00:07:30.810 --> 00:07:32.490 line:80%
200,000 piculs of grain.

00:07:51.050 --> 00:07:51.930 line:80%
Pardon me.

00:07:54.810 --> 00:07:57.209 line:80%
With our Yixiang Restaurant doing so well,

00:07:58.340 --> 00:08:01.740 line:80%
it's inevitable that some jealous rivals

00:08:02.420 --> 00:08:03.880 line:80%
cause trouble in the dark.

00:08:10.490 --> 00:08:11.780 line:80%
No wonder Manager Yu

00:08:12.170 --> 00:08:15.230 line:80%
turned down my request
to book the whole place earlier.

00:08:15.300 --> 00:08:17.660 line:80%
Apparently, my business
wasn't enough to interest you guys.

00:08:17.660 --> 00:08:18.460 line:80%
Alright then.

00:08:19.250 --> 00:08:20.900 line:80%
Let's talk another day.

00:08:31.710 --> 00:08:32.420 line:80%
Where is he?

00:08:33.459 --> 00:08:34.130 line:80%
Gone.

00:08:34.250 --> 00:08:35.180 line:80%
Gone?

00:08:36.530 --> 00:08:38.229 line:80%
He gave up just like that?

00:08:38.490 --> 00:08:39.300 line:80%
Zheng.

00:08:39.320 --> 00:08:41.300 line:80%
My 30 taels were really well spent.

00:08:51.770 --> 00:08:53.290 line:80%
What happened, Master?

00:08:56.370 --> 00:08:57.570 line:80%
You won't believe it—

00:08:58.100 --> 00:08:59.940 line:80%
I just ran into a dead man,

00:09:00.290 --> 00:09:03.150 line:80%
and that woman actually claimed
he was her husband.

00:09:04.130 --> 00:09:05.650 line:80%
Master, you mean...

00:09:16.100 --> 00:09:18.860 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an, Xie Zheng.

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:21.000 line:80%
Xie Zheng?

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:23.720 line:80%
Isn't he dead?

00:09:27.770 --> 00:09:29.900 line:80%
If the Marquis of Wu'an is still alive,

00:09:30.290 --> 00:09:33.150 line:80%
I'm afraid Lord Changxin's plan
won't go smoothly.

00:09:35.130 --> 00:09:36.850 line:80%
That smart father of mine

00:09:37.010 --> 00:09:40.440 line:80%
intended to use the move of bandits
stealing military grain

00:09:40.820 --> 00:09:42.200 line:80%
to drive out refugees and create panic,

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:43.340 line:80%
and then finish the operation.

00:09:43.340 --> 00:09:44.460 line:80%
But now,

00:09:45.100 --> 00:09:46.770 line:80%
not only is the Marquis of Wu'an not dead,

00:09:46.770 --> 00:09:49.830 line:80%
but he even knows we purchased
200,000 piculs of grain.

00:09:50.390 --> 00:09:52.720 line:80%
Obviously, he's been prepared all along.

00:09:53.460 --> 00:09:55.920 line:80%
It's still hard to say who will win
in the end.

00:09:56.220 --> 00:09:59.430 line:80%
This game is getting
more and more interesting.

00:10:01.850 --> 00:10:05.150 line:80%
Back then, you intentionally
leaked information, Master,

00:10:05.150 --> 00:10:06.290 line:80%
to lead the Marquis of Wu'an
to investigate

00:10:06.290 --> 00:10:08.410 line:80%
the Jinzhou Massacre from 16 years ago

00:10:08.410 --> 00:10:11.220 line:80%
because you believed Prime Minister Wei
wouldn't allow him to reopen the case.

00:10:11.220 --> 00:10:12.610 line:80%
Your plan was to use Prime Minister Wei

00:10:12.610 --> 00:10:15.010 line:80%
to get rid of that serious threat
Xie Zheng.

00:10:15.370 --> 00:10:17.460 line:80%
But now, he's still alive...

00:10:18.440 --> 00:10:20.340 line:80%
Should we reveal his whereabouts

00:10:20.340 --> 00:10:21.740 line:80%
to Wei Yan in secret

00:10:22.010 --> 00:10:24.940 line:80%
and try to get Wei Yan to do
the dirty work for us again?

00:10:25.010 --> 00:10:25.610 line:80%
No.

00:10:26.130 --> 00:10:27.610 line:80%
I tried to turn them against each other
back then

00:10:27.610 --> 00:10:29.580 line:80%
just to sever Wei Yan's support.

00:10:30.100 --> 00:10:32.580 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an
has never been our enemy.

00:10:32.580 --> 00:10:36.010 line:80%
Now that the rift between uncle and nephew
is a done deal,

00:10:36.010 --> 00:10:37.980 line:80%
and the Marquis of Wu'an has been
cast out to the countryside,

00:10:37.980 --> 00:10:40.440 line:80%
we can take this opportunity
to win him over.

00:10:41.650 --> 00:10:43.370 line:80%
Take my East Palace seal
and use my former identity

00:10:43.370 --> 00:10:46.430 line:80%
as the Crown Prince of the Eastern Palace
to lure him in.

00:10:47.370 --> 00:10:48.010 line:80%
Got it.

00:10:51.290 --> 00:10:52.860 line:80%
As for Manager Yu...

00:10:53.340 --> 00:10:54.130 line:80%
Her?

00:10:57.410 --> 00:10:59.670 line:80%
Just have someone keep a close eye on her.

00:11:00.400 --> 00:11:02.260 line:80%
[Yixiang Restaurant]

00:11:00.890 --> 00:11:02.700 line:80%
Come on in, ladies. This way.

00:11:04.580 --> 00:11:05.910 line:80%
Please come in, ladies.

00:11:06.220 --> 00:11:07.290 line:80%
Welcome, ladies.

00:11:19.250 --> 00:11:20.010 line:80%
Mrs. Fan.

00:11:29.250 --> 00:11:29.940 line:80%
Changyu.

00:11:30.580 --> 00:11:31.180 line:80%
Come here.

00:11:34.250 --> 00:11:34.980 line:80%
Look.

00:11:35.700 --> 00:11:36.940 line:80%
The restaurant is so lively—

00:11:36.940 --> 00:11:38.180 line:80%
it's all thanks to you.

00:11:38.180 --> 00:11:39.870 line:80%
What do you mean, thanks to me?

00:11:39.940 --> 00:11:42.100 line:80%
Ever since your husband came by,

00:11:42.100 --> 00:11:44.360 line:80%
that Qi fellow hasn't bothered me again.

00:11:44.890 --> 00:11:46.610 line:80%
I can finally focus on
running the business.

00:11:46.610 --> 00:11:47.820 line:80%
Now look—the restaurant is so lively.

00:11:47.820 --> 00:11:49.420 line:80%
Of course it's thanks to you.

00:11:50.860 --> 00:11:51.610 line:80%
Come with me.

00:11:54.460 --> 00:11:57.260 line:80%
I wonder what Chef Li is cooking
for New Year's Eve.

00:11:57.740 --> 00:11:59.800 line:80%
What are you planning to eat tonight?

00:12:01.250 --> 00:12:02.490 line:80%
Cabbage and tofu,

00:12:03.220 --> 00:12:04.060 line:80%
and stir-fried pork.

00:12:04.060 --> 00:12:04.740 line:80%
Go on.

00:12:07.340 --> 00:12:09.270 line:80%
Hello, Mother. Hello, Auntie Fan.

00:12:09.890 --> 00:12:10.460 line:80%
Sit.

00:12:12.220 --> 00:12:14.020 line:80%
What is Changning doing at home?

00:12:14.060 --> 00:12:15.100 line:80%
I miss her.

00:12:15.490 --> 00:12:16.700 line:80%
How about after New Year's Eve,

00:12:16.700 --> 00:12:19.300 line:80%
you come over to our place
and hang out with her?

00:12:20.730 --> 00:12:22.240 line:80%
Mother, can I go?

00:12:24.370 --> 00:12:25.210 line:80%
Fine.

00:12:25.740 --> 00:12:26.770 line:80%
Just this once.

00:12:27.860 --> 00:12:28.820 line:80%
Changning said

00:12:28.850 --> 00:12:30.780 line:80%
she'd show me her family heirloom.

00:12:31.100 --> 00:12:33.530 line:80%
Family heirloom?

00:12:37.180 --> 00:12:39.310 line:80%
She probably meant our butcher knife.

00:12:39.770 --> 00:12:41.570 line:80%
I guess that won't be necessary.

00:12:41.860 --> 00:12:43.020 line:80%
That's so cool!

00:12:43.040 --> 00:12:44.900 line:80%
So it's actually a butcher knife!

00:12:48.340 --> 00:12:50.180 line:80%
I have things to discuss with Auntie Fan.

00:12:50.180 --> 00:12:51.240 line:80%
Go study first.

00:12:55.700 --> 00:12:56.340 line:80%
Let's go.

00:12:59.460 --> 00:13:00.290 line:80%
Qianqian.

00:13:00.770 --> 00:13:03.140 line:80%
Aren't you a bit too strict with Bao'er?

00:13:04.290 --> 00:13:05.130 line:80%
Not at all.

00:13:05.530 --> 00:13:07.390 line:80%
I just want him to succeed in life.

00:13:10.130 --> 00:13:11.090 line:80%
Changyu.

00:13:11.650 --> 00:13:13.000 line:80%
Tomorrow is New Year's Eve,

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:14.790 line:80%
and you'll surely be swamped.

00:13:15.490 --> 00:13:18.940 line:80%
I want to wish you in advance
a smooth and happy year ahead.

00:13:19.610 --> 00:13:20.920 line:80%
I'm not a child.

00:13:20.940 --> 00:13:22.670 line:80%
Why give me a lucky money pouch?

00:13:23.460 --> 00:13:24.860 line:80%
Us girls

00:13:24.860 --> 00:13:26.530 line:80%
are forever young.

00:13:26.740 --> 00:13:28.200 line:80%
Come on. Let's get a drink.

00:13:28.740 --> 00:13:30.250 line:80%
Drinking at noon?

00:13:31.010 --> 00:13:32.740 line:80%
We women drink when we feel like it,

00:13:32.740 --> 00:13:33.740 line:80%
not when the clock says so.

00:13:33.740 --> 00:13:35.100 line:80%
If not now, then when?

00:13:37.280 --> 00:13:41.130 line:80%
[Overflowing Joy and Good Fortune]

00:13:41.980 --> 00:13:43.010 line:80%
Cheers!

00:13:47.740 --> 00:13:48.610 line:80%
Qianqian.

00:13:49.250 --> 00:13:51.580 line:80%
The last time I was this happy

00:13:52.130 --> 00:13:54.700 line:80%
was the day I married Yan Zheng.

00:13:58.490 --> 00:13:59.410 line:80%
Changyu,

00:14:00.340 --> 00:14:03.340 line:80%
you've been married for
quite some time now.

00:14:04.180 --> 00:14:05.920 line:80%
That husband of yours—

00:14:06.070 --> 00:14:07.600 line:80%
are you satisfied with him?

00:14:11.250 --> 00:14:13.940 line:80%
He's not just all show, is he?

00:14:14.700 --> 00:14:16.500 line:80%
All show?

00:14:17.410 --> 00:14:19.650 line:80%
Yan Zheng is pure gold—

00:14:20.230 --> 00:14:22.490 line:80%
through and through.

00:14:23.130 --> 00:14:24.750 line:80%
He's that good?

00:14:25.700 --> 00:14:26.700 line:80%
I'm going to find someone

00:14:26.700 --> 00:14:27.820 line:80%
to beat Granny Kang up.

00:14:27.820 --> 00:14:30.950 line:80%
She said you two hadn't even
consummated your marriage.

00:14:31.220 --> 00:14:33.220 line:80%
You were talking about
consummating the marriage?

00:14:33.220 --> 00:14:34.480 line:80%
What else would I mean?

00:14:34.770 --> 00:14:36.700 line:80%
Granny Kang really has a potty mouth.

00:14:36.700 --> 00:14:38.700 line:80%
It's fine. I'll beat her up.
I can afford the damages.

00:14:38.700 --> 00:14:39.430 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:14:39.530 --> 00:14:40.150 line:80%
Qianqian.

00:14:41.490 --> 00:14:43.100 line:80%
Actually...

00:14:43.820 --> 00:14:46.370 line:80%
She wasn't entirely wrong.

00:14:48.890 --> 00:14:51.940 line:80%
Which part wasn't wrong?

00:14:54.060 --> 00:14:55.410 line:80%
One day,

00:14:56.130 --> 00:14:59.820 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao locked the two of us in a room.

00:15:01.130 --> 00:15:03.370 line:80%
He probably wanted to kiss me.

00:15:05.490 --> 00:15:07.350 line:80%
Did you eat tangerine peel candy?

00:15:07.610 --> 00:15:10.120 line:80%
You smell like tangerine peel candy.

00:15:10.650 --> 00:15:13.410 line:80%
Do you want some now?

00:15:18.650 --> 00:15:19.490 line:80%
And then?

00:15:20.250 --> 00:15:21.850 line:80%
Then...

00:15:23.890 --> 00:15:25.340 line:80%
We had a fight.

00:15:31.250 --> 00:15:33.050 line:80%
So you two are actually serious?

00:15:41.940 --> 00:15:44.010 line:80%
Actually, I know deep down

00:15:46.290 --> 00:15:47.250 line:80%
that

00:15:50.010 --> 00:15:51.650 line:80%
he'd leave sooner or later.

00:15:55.770 --> 00:15:58.460 line:80%
I've hinted at it several times,

00:16:02.180 --> 00:16:04.240 line:80%
yet he never gave a different answer.

00:16:11.820 --> 00:16:13.890 line:80%
Your man does seem to be

00:16:14.860 --> 00:16:16.740 line:80%
too big a fish for your small pond.

00:16:20.490 --> 00:16:21.180 line:80%
It's okay.

00:16:21.740 --> 00:16:23.140 line:80%
If he insists on leaving,

00:16:23.490 --> 00:16:26.250 line:80%
just have a baby with him before he goes.

00:16:26.770 --> 00:16:27.650 line:80%
Think about it—

00:16:27.820 --> 00:16:29.980 line:80%
if the child turns out
as good-looking as him,

00:16:29.980 --> 00:16:31.980 line:80%
that would be a kind of blessing too.

00:16:34.770 --> 00:16:37.220 line:80%
That won't do, right?

00:16:38.580 --> 00:16:41.510 line:80%
Wouldn't that basically be
taking advantage of him?

00:16:41.820 --> 00:16:44.100 line:80%
You know the saying, "you can't catch a wolf
without sacrificing a lamb."

00:16:44.100 --> 00:16:45.250 line:80%
Wait—actually, in this case it's:

00:16:45.250 --> 00:16:47.980 line:80%
you won't get a baby
without feeding the wolf.

00:16:52.610 --> 00:16:53.340 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:16:53.770 --> 00:16:55.820 line:80%
Leave this to me.

00:17:05.610 --> 00:17:10.040 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:17:18.659 --> 00:17:22.290 line:80%
Zhao Xun, the shopkeeper of
Lin'an Rice Shop, is here to visit.

00:17:25.850 --> 00:17:27.169 line:80%
It's freezing cold.

00:17:27.220 --> 00:17:29.350 line:80%
Won't Your Lordship invite me in?

00:17:39.180 --> 00:17:40.040 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:17:40.900 --> 00:17:41.760 line:80%
Your Lordship?

00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:51.530 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:17:50.570 --> 00:17:51.970 line:80%
How did you recognize me?

00:17:53.050 --> 00:17:55.570 line:80%
I used to do business
in Jizhou and Yanzhou.

00:17:56.090 --> 00:17:58.950 line:80%
I was lucky enough to
have seen Your Lordship there.

00:18:01.940 --> 00:18:02.770 line:80%
So?

00:18:04.010 --> 00:18:06.140 line:80%
Why are you here today?

00:18:09.900 --> 00:18:12.040 line:80%
Your Xie family has always been
loyal and virtuous,

00:18:12.040 --> 00:18:14.900 line:80%
which is a fact
known throughout the whole country.

00:18:14.980 --> 00:18:16.450 line:80%
Yet Heaven is unjust,

00:18:16.770 --> 00:18:18.900 line:80%
allowing evildoers to bring you harm.

00:18:19.460 --> 00:18:22.260 line:80%
I too feel indignation
on Your Lordship's behalf.

00:18:25.290 --> 00:18:27.150 line:80%
I don't understand what you mean.

00:18:27.800 --> 00:18:30.660 line:80%
Wasn't the reason Wei Yan
hunted Your Lordship down

00:18:30.660 --> 00:18:31.830 line:80%
because you were investigating

00:18:31.830 --> 00:18:34.030 line:80%
the Jinzhou Massacre from 16 years ago?

00:18:40.900 --> 00:18:42.380 line:80%
Who exactly are you?

00:18:58.340 --> 00:19:00.430 line:80%
[Chengde Heavenly Treasure]

00:19:00.740 --> 00:19:02.020 line:80%
Sixteen years ago,

00:19:02.900 --> 00:19:04.830 line:80%
in that fire at the Eastern Palace—

00:19:05.420 --> 00:19:07.220 line:80%
I was one of the lucky survivors.

00:19:09.220 --> 00:19:11.380 line:80%
Wei Yan is a treacherous official
in power,

00:19:11.380 --> 00:19:13.040 line:80%
supporting a puppet emperor.

00:19:13.250 --> 00:19:14.510 line:80%
We are a group of people

00:19:14.940 --> 00:19:16.700 line:80%
who want to restore order.

00:19:18.570 --> 00:19:19.530 line:80%
So,

00:19:20.570 --> 00:19:21.790 line:80%
do you have any proof?

00:19:23.180 --> 00:19:26.360 line:80%
Crown Prince Chengde
and Your Lordship's father

00:19:26.620 --> 00:19:28.480 line:80%
both died tragically in Jinzhou.

00:19:29.460 --> 00:19:31.050 line:80%
Then the Emperor abdicated,

00:19:31.050 --> 00:19:32.900 line:80%
and the Eastern Palace caught fire.

00:19:32.900 --> 00:19:35.560 line:80%
All these suspicious events
pointed to Wei Yan.

00:19:35.770 --> 00:19:38.140 line:80%
Your Lordship's father and the Crown Prince
both died in battle,

00:19:38.140 --> 00:19:41.850 line:80%
and their bodies were hung on the city wall
by the Beijue people for 3 days.

00:19:41.850 --> 00:19:44.850 line:80%
Doesn't Your Lordship want to
avenge this blood feud?

00:19:48.940 --> 00:19:52.220 line:80%
Your Lordship had just started
reinvestigating the Jinzhou Massacre,

00:19:52.220 --> 00:19:53.660 line:80%
and you immediately got hunted down

00:19:53.660 --> 00:19:54.940 line:80%
and ended up here—

00:19:55.330 --> 00:19:56.940 line:80%
isn't that proof enough?

00:20:06.530 --> 00:20:07.210 line:80%
Not enough.

00:20:18.180 --> 00:20:19.380 line:80%
We also found out that

00:20:20.050 --> 00:20:21.770 line:80%
Wei Yan sent his Suicide Warriors

00:20:21.770 --> 00:20:23.770 line:80%
across the Capital and 17 prefectures

00:20:23.770 --> 00:20:25.030 line:80%
to kill over 10 people—

00:20:26.330 --> 00:20:28.590 line:80%
all retainers who once worked for Wei Yan

00:20:29.010 --> 00:20:30.450 line:80%
and later retired.

00:20:30.530 --> 00:20:32.620 line:80%
What exactly does the Fan family have

00:20:32.620 --> 00:20:35.620 line:80%
that's worth the Wei family's
Iron Suicide Warriors coming here for?

00:20:35.620 --> 00:20:37.080 line:80%
It was the Prime Minister.

00:20:37.250 --> 00:20:38.980 line:80%
He sent me here to find a letter.

00:20:40.180 --> 00:20:43.110 line:80%
So Fan Erniu must have also
worked for Wei Yan before,

00:20:43.580 --> 00:20:45.710 line:80%
which is why he kept being hunted down.

00:20:46.700 --> 00:20:47.560 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:20:48.290 --> 00:20:50.170 line:80%
Wei Yan is immensely powerful now,

00:20:50.170 --> 00:20:52.420 line:80%
with ambitions that could
overshadow the heavens.

00:20:52.420 --> 00:20:53.740 line:80%
To bring him down,

00:20:54.180 --> 00:20:56.180 line:80%
doesn't Your Lordship need an ally?

00:20:56.940 --> 00:20:58.570 line:80%
How can I trust you?

00:20:58.980 --> 00:21:00.710 line:80%
How can Your Lordship trust me?

00:21:03.250 --> 00:21:04.580 line:80%
Give me a deposit first.

00:21:05.220 --> 00:21:06.220 line:80%
What deposit?

00:21:08.380 --> 00:21:09.850 line:80%
200,000 piculs of grain—

00:21:10.940 --> 00:21:12.070 line:80%
how does that sound?

00:21:15.570 --> 00:21:17.810 line:80%
It seems he really knows about

00:21:17.810 --> 00:21:21.070 line:80%
my grain collection from all across
Jizhou and Chongzhou.

00:21:22.140 --> 00:21:23.850 line:80%
We bought from many sources,

00:21:24.250 --> 00:21:26.510 line:80%
with over 100 grain merchants involved.

00:21:26.620 --> 00:21:28.660 line:80%
How did he know so accurately?

00:21:29.010 --> 00:21:32.490 line:80%
I'd actually like to ask you that.

00:21:33.900 --> 00:21:36.230 line:80%
Forgive me, Master. It was my negligence.

00:21:38.530 --> 00:21:40.700 line:80%
But it's good that
he's willing to name his terms.

00:21:40.700 --> 00:21:42.160 line:80%
It's business, after all.

00:21:43.140 --> 00:21:45.250 line:80%
Once he quotes a price, we can talk.

00:21:48.660 --> 00:21:50.010 line:80%
200,000 piculs...

00:21:50.570 --> 00:21:51.330 line:80%
Master,

00:21:51.570 --> 00:21:53.480 line:80%
the grain from all across
Chongzhou and Jizhou

00:21:53.480 --> 00:21:55.530 line:80%
has almost been emptied by us
these past months.

00:21:55.530 --> 00:21:58.060 line:80%
He didn't ask you to give it
all at once, did he?

00:22:00.250 --> 00:22:02.740 line:80%
Father never cared about me,

00:22:02.980 --> 00:22:05.850 line:80%
and the position of Crown Prince
was meant for Sui Yuanqing.

00:22:05.850 --> 00:22:08.780 line:80%
But if we can gain the support of
the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:22:09.740 --> 00:22:11.600 line:80%
our chances of success will soar.

00:22:12.050 --> 00:22:13.580 line:80%
What if the Marquis of Wu'an

00:22:13.610 --> 00:22:15.390 line:80%
doesn't believe your identity,

00:22:15.390 --> 00:22:17.220 line:80%
takes the grain, and turns against us,
Master?

00:22:17.220 --> 00:22:18.180 line:80%
What then?

00:22:18.460 --> 00:22:19.390 line:80%
Turn against us?

00:22:19.940 --> 00:22:21.330 line:80%
Who else can he turn to?

00:22:22.010 --> 00:22:24.340 line:80%
Can he possibly go back to
work for Wei Yan?

00:22:25.290 --> 00:22:27.940 line:80%
As long as he's willing to help me
wholeheartedly,

00:22:27.940 --> 00:22:29.660 line:80%
let alone 200,000 piculs of grain—

00:22:29.660 --> 00:22:31.090 line:80%
I can even grant all 4 prefectures

00:22:31.090 --> 00:22:33.020 line:80%
of the Northwest to him as his fief.

00:22:33.180 --> 00:22:33.910 line:80%
Understood.

00:22:34.330 --> 00:22:35.860 line:80%
I'll see to it immediately.

00:22:45.940 --> 00:22:47.810 line:80%
Wei Yan, oh Wei Yan.

00:22:49.620 --> 00:22:50.940 line:80%
You will soon

00:22:50.940 --> 00:22:53.620 line:80%
be bitten by the ungrateful wolf

00:22:54.570 --> 00:22:55.920 line:80%
you raised yourself.

00:22:59.740 --> 00:23:00.670 line:80%
Prime Minister.

00:23:01.700 --> 00:23:05.230 line:80%
I was investigating
Grand Tutor Li's dealings with the rebels,

00:23:05.530 --> 00:23:06.660 line:80%
and I accidentally found out
that when the Marquis of Wu'an

00:23:06.660 --> 00:23:09.860 line:80%
was reinvestigating the Jinzhou cases
from 16 years ago,

00:23:10.140 --> 00:23:13.670 line:80%
it was exactly Lord Changxin's people
who plotted against him.

00:23:16.980 --> 00:23:19.770 line:80%
If Xie Zheng didn't exist in this world,

00:23:20.770 --> 00:23:24.500 line:80%
Lord Changxin would have
one less major threat on the battlefield.

00:23:26.010 --> 00:23:28.010 line:80%
The Sui family is

00:23:28.850 --> 00:23:31.010 line:80%
trying to ruin my great plans.

00:23:34.900 --> 00:23:36.010 line:80%
There's one more thing.

00:23:36.010 --> 00:23:37.900 line:80%
Li Huai'an was recalled to the Capital
by Grand Tutor Li

00:23:37.900 --> 00:23:39.300 line:80%
for some unknown reason.

00:23:40.980 --> 00:23:42.620 line:80%
With Princess Royal back in the Capital,

00:23:42.620 --> 00:23:45.420 line:80%
that old coot probably wants to
push the marriage,

00:23:46.140 --> 00:23:49.270 line:80%
so he hurried to
recall his eldest legitimate grandson.

00:23:50.850 --> 00:23:51.940 line:80%
Just leave him be.

00:23:53.180 --> 00:23:55.490 line:80%
Write to He Jingyuan immediately

00:23:55.810 --> 00:23:57.660 line:80%
and tell him to defend Lucheng
to the death.

00:23:57.660 --> 00:23:59.990 line:80%
That's the place for the decisive battle.

00:24:01.510 --> 00:24:05.260 line:80%
[New Year's Eve]

00:24:13.980 --> 00:24:15.260 line:80%
Happy New Year.

00:24:15.290 --> 00:24:16.620 line:80%
Come on, everyone, time for dinner.

00:24:16.620 --> 00:24:17.910 line:80%
Coming. Coming.

00:24:18.180 --> 00:24:19.640 line:80%
Happy New Year, Mrs. Wang.

00:24:23.530 --> 00:24:24.770 line:80%
Happy New Year, Mrs. San.

00:24:24.770 --> 00:24:26.010 line:80%
Happy New Year, Mr. San.

00:24:26.010 --> 00:24:27.250 line:80%
Happy New Year.

00:24:27.650 --> 00:24:30.690 line:80%
[Chunfeng Tofu Shop]

00:24:28.290 --> 00:24:29.530 line:80%
Happy New Year to you.

00:24:32.770 --> 00:24:34.370 line:80%
Keep writing. Keep writing.

00:24:34.810 --> 00:24:35.540 line:80%
Horizontal.

00:24:36.810 --> 00:24:38.140 line:80%
Horizontal, vertical.

00:24:39.330 --> 00:24:39.940 line:80%
Vertical.

00:24:41.460 --> 00:24:45.010 line:80%
Horizontal with a turn,
left-falling, right-falling.

00:24:51.850 --> 00:24:54.420 line:80%
Sister, Zheng is teaching me how to write.

00:24:54.740 --> 00:24:55.460 line:80%
Good girl.

00:25:00.770 --> 00:25:03.570 line:80%
Do you know how to write
Spring Festival couplets?

00:25:05.660 --> 00:25:09.090 line:80%
My mother used to write them every year.

00:25:09.490 --> 00:25:12.150 line:80%
Can you write Spring Festival couplets,
Zheng?

00:25:12.180 --> 00:25:13.180 line:80%
Get me the paper.

00:25:13.660 --> 00:25:14.290 line:80%
Okay.

00:25:29.660 --> 00:25:30.990 line:80%
You ground too much ink.

00:25:33.480 --> 00:25:35.710 line:80%
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

00:25:33.770 --> 00:25:35.300 line:80%
Then write a few more pairs.

00:25:35.460 --> 00:25:37.090 line:80%
We can give some to Mrs. Zhao
and the others,

00:25:36.750 --> 00:25:37.970 line:80%
♪ With very pale colors ♪

00:25:37.850 --> 00:25:40.260 line:80%
and we can put the rest on the doorframes
of all these rooms.

00:25:38.750 --> 00:25:41.710 line:80%
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

00:25:40.490 --> 00:25:41.290 line:80%
For good omen.

00:25:42.170 --> 00:25:44.660 line:80%
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

00:25:42.940 --> 00:25:43.490 line:80%
Alright.

00:25:45.410 --> 00:25:46.890 line:80%
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

00:25:47.570 --> 00:25:51.730 line:80%
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

00:25:55.180 --> 00:25:57.740 line:80%
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

00:25:58.450 --> 00:26:00.060 line:80%
♪ The light shines ♪

00:26:00.770 --> 00:26:03.470 line:80%
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

00:26:02.810 --> 00:26:04.960 line:80%
[Sprouting Grass]

00:26:03.940 --> 00:26:06.550 line:80%
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

00:26:07.170 --> 00:26:08.910 line:80%
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

00:26:09.360 --> 00:26:14.270 line:80%
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

00:26:16.680 --> 00:26:17.840 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love ♪

00:26:17.870 --> 00:26:20.560 line:80%
♪ Will never end ♪

00:26:21.230 --> 00:26:22.200 line:80%
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

00:26:22.230 --> 00:26:24.490 line:80%
♪ For a lifetime ♪

00:26:25.130 --> 00:26:29.180 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:26:26.380 --> 00:26:28.460 line:80%
D-Did I accidentally touch you?

00:26:29.220 --> 00:26:31.180 line:80%
It's fine. I just got a bit too much ink
on the brush.

00:26:29.590 --> 00:26:33.290 line:80%
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

00:26:34.080 --> 00:26:35.010 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

00:26:35.030 --> 00:26:37.540 line:80%
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

00:26:37.060 --> 00:26:46.150 line:80%
[Be a Good Person]

00:26:38.820 --> 00:26:39.760 line:80%
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

00:26:39.290 --> 00:26:40.700 line:80%
Your calligraphy is really good.

00:26:39.780 --> 00:26:42.130 line:80%
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

00:26:42.930 --> 00:26:46.820 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:26:45.010 --> 00:26:46.090 line:80%
What a pity.

00:26:47.140 --> 00:26:48.010 line:80%
But it's okay.

00:26:47.300 --> 00:26:57.940 line:80%
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

00:26:49.400 --> 00:26:53.830 line:80%
[As ice thaws, the springs awaken]
[With snow gone, new grass sprouts]

00:26:49.490 --> 00:26:52.890 line:80%
I'll just put this pair
on the door of Changning's and my room.

00:26:53.090 --> 00:26:55.140 line:80%
Ice something...

00:26:56.090 --> 00:26:57.890 line:80%
Spring something something...

00:26:59.220 --> 00:27:03.530 line:80%
Snow something... New grass sprouts.

00:27:04.290 --> 00:27:06.050 line:80%
As ice thaws, the springs awaken.

00:27:06.050 --> 00:27:07.980 line:80%
With snow gone, new grass sprouts.

00:27:09.380 --> 00:27:12.770 line:80%
When my mother wrote
Spring Festival couplets,

00:27:12.940 --> 00:27:14.160 line:80%
she didn't like writing those

00:27:14.160 --> 00:27:16.220 line:80%
clichéd auspicious phrases either.

00:27:16.660 --> 00:27:17.660 line:80%
Do you like these?

00:27:20.690 --> 00:27:24.310 line:80%
[Be a Good Person]

00:27:43.180 --> 00:27:44.380 line:80%
You know how to paint?

00:27:46.770 --> 00:27:47.660 line:80%
Only a little.

00:27:54.850 --> 00:27:55.810 line:80%
That's enough.

00:27:58.770 --> 00:28:00.850 line:80%
If you go and sell
your calligraphy and paintings out there,

00:28:00.850 --> 00:28:02.980 line:80%
you'll definitely make a lot of money.

00:28:06.810 --> 00:28:08.870 line:80%
I don't paint what doesn't please me.

00:28:11.940 --> 00:28:13.740 line:80%
I want to write something too.

00:28:15.970 --> 00:28:17.300 line:80%
Write a top scroll then.

00:28:19.220 --> 00:28:21.420 line:80%
Come on, Changning,
write a top scroll.

00:28:23.620 --> 00:28:24.880 line:80%
What should you write?

00:28:25.940 --> 00:28:27.180 line:80%
What should I write?

00:28:38.770 --> 00:28:40.050 line:80%
Just write this.

00:28:46.280 --> 00:28:50.230 line:80%
[You'll Be Rich]

00:28:48.530 --> 00:28:49.790 line:80%
How's this top scroll?

00:28:53.250 --> 00:28:54.380 line:80%
Just like...

00:28:55.660 --> 00:28:57.260 line:80%
Joining a dog's tail to sable fur.

00:28:57.260 --> 00:29:01.680 line:80%
[You'll Be Rich]

00:29:00.230 --> 00:29:02.090 line:80%
That means it's very good, right?

00:29:06.530 --> 00:29:08.390 line:80%
That means it's very good, right?

00:29:10.400 --> 00:29:11.550 line:80%
It's perfect.

00:29:12.450 --> 00:29:15.510 line:80%
[You'll Be Rich]

00:29:16.180 --> 00:29:17.830 line:80%
I wrote it too well.

00:29:18.180 --> 00:29:19.330 line:80%
I'm amazing.

00:29:21.570 --> 00:29:23.570 line:80%
Oh right, we're missing the falcon.

00:29:29.250 --> 00:29:30.300 line:80%
Good falcon,

00:29:30.660 --> 00:29:32.860 line:80%
let's celebrate the New Year together.

00:29:37.490 --> 00:29:39.290 line:80%
With the falcon's claw print,

00:29:39.460 --> 00:29:42.190 line:80%
our family is complete.

00:29:45.590 --> 00:29:48.150 line:80%
[You'll Be Rich]

00:29:46.330 --> 00:29:47.010 line:80%
Look.

00:29:50.250 --> 00:29:51.180 line:80%
Dear.

00:29:51.530 --> 00:29:52.970 line:80%
Lower. Lower.

00:29:53.850 --> 00:29:54.770 line:80%
Alright, alright. Right there.

00:29:54.770 --> 00:29:56.290 line:80%
Don't move. Don't move further. That's it.

00:29:56.290 --> 00:29:58.420 line:80%
-Alright.
-Let's go check on Changyu.

00:29:59.900 --> 00:30:00.620 line:80%
Okay.

00:30:03.010 --> 00:30:03.770 line:80%
Dear.

00:30:04.460 --> 00:30:05.740 line:80%
How is the calligraphy?

00:30:05.740 --> 00:30:07.150 line:80%
It's beautiful.

00:30:07.170 --> 00:30:09.660 line:80%
-I've never seen such nice calligraphy before.
-He wrote this, right?

00:30:09.660 --> 00:30:12.740 line:80%
-I guess so.
-You're illiterate. Can you really understand it?

00:30:12.740 --> 00:30:14.050 line:80%
I may not be able to read,

00:30:14.050 --> 00:30:16.270 line:80%
but I can tell this calligraphy
is valuable.

00:30:16.270 --> 00:30:17.740 line:80%
Look how square and upright
the characters are.

00:30:17.740 --> 00:30:18.660 line:80%
So neat and proper.

00:30:18.660 --> 00:30:20.590 line:80%
It's obvious it's worth a fortune.

00:30:21.200 --> 00:30:22.980 line:80%
Mr. Zhao, Mrs. Zhao.

00:30:23.250 --> 00:30:25.140 line:80%
The couplets are written so well.

00:30:25.380 --> 00:30:26.330 line:80%
Who wrote these?

00:30:26.330 --> 00:30:28.790 line:80%
Changyu's husband wrote all of these.

00:30:32.380 --> 00:30:33.510 line:80%
Changyu's husband.

00:30:35.700 --> 00:30:36.530 line:80%
Changyu,

00:30:37.380 --> 00:30:40.150 line:80%
your husband writes really nice couplets—

00:30:40.250 --> 00:30:42.890 line:80%
even better than the ones Scholar Song

00:30:42.920 --> 00:30:44.290 line:80%
wrote in previous years.

00:30:44.290 --> 00:30:45.460 line:80%
That's why I say

00:30:45.460 --> 00:30:47.420 line:80%
our Changyu has good taste.

00:30:48.330 --> 00:30:50.180 line:80%
Can he write a pair for me too?

00:30:52.660 --> 00:30:54.810 line:80%
-Yeah. Write a pair for us too.
-Write for all of us.

00:30:54.810 --> 00:30:55.570 line:80%
Sis.

00:30:55.900 --> 00:30:56.660 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:30:56.660 --> 00:30:58.860 line:80%
We ran out of red paper for the couplets.

00:30:59.250 --> 00:31:00.660 line:80%
Oh, red paper for the couplets?

00:31:00.660 --> 00:31:03.620 line:80%
I've got plenty of red paper at home
from previous years.

00:31:03.620 --> 00:31:05.290 line:80%
I've got some at home too.

00:31:05.290 --> 00:31:06.700 line:80%
-I have some too.
-Me too.

00:31:06.940 --> 00:31:07.570 line:80%
Alright.

00:31:08.700 --> 00:31:09.900 line:80%
Bring the paper over.

00:31:10.380 --> 00:31:10.940 line:80%
Alright!

00:31:11.280 --> 00:31:12.660 line:80%
Quick, go get the red paper.

00:31:12.660 --> 00:31:13.620 line:80%
Okay, thanks.

00:31:13.620 --> 00:31:14.900 line:80%
See you in a bit.

00:31:15.330 --> 00:31:16.090 line:80%
Let's go.

00:31:25.660 --> 00:31:26.940 line:80%
If you aren't willing,

00:31:26.940 --> 00:31:28.250 line:80%
you didn't have to agree.

00:31:28.250 --> 00:31:29.450 line:80%
Don't worry about me.

00:31:30.420 --> 00:31:31.290 line:80%
I am willing.

00:31:33.460 --> 00:31:35.090 line:80%
You just said

00:31:35.090 --> 00:31:37.490 line:80%
you wouldn't paint what didn't please you.

00:31:40.250 --> 00:31:41.720 line:80%
Now it pleases you?

00:31:42.220 --> 00:31:43.020 line:80%
Grind the ink.

00:31:43.810 --> 00:31:44.460 line:80%
Changyu.

00:31:45.490 --> 00:31:46.460 line:80%
Mrs. Zhuang.

00:31:46.460 --> 00:31:48.250 line:80%
Here's some homemade puffed rice candy—

00:31:48.250 --> 00:31:49.910 line:80%
a little snack for Changning.

00:31:50.810 --> 00:31:51.480 line:80%
But...

00:31:51.620 --> 00:31:52.290 line:80%
Take it.

00:31:52.290 --> 00:31:55.220 line:80%
Changyu, I heard your husband
was writing Spring Festival couplets for people.

00:31:55.220 --> 00:31:57.810 line:80%
Our family hasn't gotten ours written yet,
either,

00:31:57.810 --> 00:32:00.060 line:80%
so I boldly came along.

00:32:00.660 --> 00:32:02.500 line:80%
It's nothing fancy,

00:32:02.850 --> 00:32:05.940 line:80%
just some freshly ground tofu
for you to taste.

00:32:08.050 --> 00:32:08.770 line:80%
Ladies,

00:32:09.140 --> 00:32:10.090 line:80%
please have a seat first.

00:32:10.090 --> 00:32:11.150 line:80%
Alright, alright.

00:32:12.850 --> 00:32:13.380 line:80%
Thank you.

00:32:13.380 --> 00:32:14.180 line:80%
Here's the red paper I brought.

00:32:14.180 --> 00:32:15.310 line:80%
Alright, thank you.

00:32:37.050 --> 00:32:39.810 line:80%
Harmony brings peace to all frontiers.

00:32:40.260 --> 00:32:41.190 line:80%
Done.

00:32:41.810 --> 00:32:42.670 line:80%
It's finished.

00:32:45.050 --> 00:32:47.010 line:80%
"Lanterns shine on homes to celebrate
the prosperous year."

00:32:47.010 --> 00:32:49.980 line:80%
"The ox carries spring to plow
the green fields."

00:32:49.980 --> 00:32:51.900 line:80%
It means that when spring comes
next year,

00:32:51.900 --> 00:32:53.290 line:80%
there will be a bumper harvest,

00:32:53.290 --> 00:32:55.890 line:80%
and the whole family
will be happy and healthy.

00:33:03.660 --> 00:33:04.900 line:80%
Though storm and darkness fill the sky

00:33:04.900 --> 00:33:06.770 line:80%
and the rooster crows without end,

00:33:06.770 --> 00:33:08.090 line:80%
now that I have met you—

00:33:08.180 --> 00:33:09.910 line:80%
how could my heart not rejoice?

00:33:10.460 --> 00:33:11.570 line:80%
The meaning of this poem line is that

00:33:11.570 --> 00:33:14.470 line:80%
amidst the gloom and pouring rain,

00:33:14.570 --> 00:33:16.140 line:80%
the roosters crow in panic.

00:33:17.220 --> 00:33:19.700 line:80%
Yet, precisely in this chaotic moment,

00:33:20.980 --> 00:33:22.200 line:80%
I glance around,

00:33:23.290 --> 00:33:24.650 line:80%
and I catch sight of her.

00:33:25.740 --> 00:33:28.250 line:80%
It's like parting the clouds and mist,

00:33:28.380 --> 00:33:30.770 line:80%
and a beam of light falls upon me—

00:33:32.740 --> 00:33:34.210 line:80%
warm and radiant,

00:33:34.940 --> 00:33:36.470 line:80%
filling my heart with joy.

00:33:37.660 --> 00:33:39.850 line:80%
When I heard him recite this line before,

00:33:39.850 --> 00:33:41.580 line:80%
I just thought it sounded nice,

00:33:41.770 --> 00:33:44.030 line:80%
but I had no idea
what was so good about it.

00:33:44.980 --> 00:33:46.360 line:80%
Until just now,

00:33:47.530 --> 00:33:49.730 line:80%
when he turned his head and looked at me.

00:33:51.770 --> 00:33:52.900 line:80%
In that instant,

00:33:53.380 --> 00:33:55.580 line:80%
the courtyard fell completely silent.

00:33:56.620 --> 00:34:00.400 line:80%
Even the falling snow seemed lighter,

00:34:01.810 --> 00:34:03.500 line:80%
and even the wind blowing over

00:34:03.660 --> 00:34:06.090 line:80%
felt softer and gentler.

00:34:07.330 --> 00:34:09.370 line:80%
It was like the sun
on the Winter Solstice—

00:34:09.370 --> 00:34:11.030 line:80%
neither slanting nor skewed,

00:34:11.580 --> 00:34:14.850 line:80%
shining perfectly on me.

00:34:15.810 --> 00:34:17.870 line:80%
It turns out when you are truly happy,

00:34:18.060 --> 00:34:19.700 line:80%
your heart sings.

00:34:20.539 --> 00:34:22.999 line:80%
Just like when you sit by the stove,

00:34:23.370 --> 00:34:25.330 line:80%
and the firewood crackles softly,

00:34:26.019 --> 00:34:29.019 line:80%
crisp and warm.

00:34:36.410 --> 00:34:37.939 line:80%
Your hand must hurt, right?

00:34:38.499 --> 00:34:39.300 line:80%
It's nothing.

00:34:39.890 --> 00:34:41.150 line:80%
Still toughing it out.

00:35:01.410 --> 00:35:03.070 line:80%
Are you here for couplets too?

00:35:06.500 --> 00:35:07.580 line:80%
Before...

00:35:08.660 --> 00:35:12.290 line:80%
Before, it was always my elder grandson,
Kang Dan, who wrote the Spring Festival couplets.

00:35:12.290 --> 00:35:14.020 line:80%
But later, he got into trouble

00:35:14.020 --> 00:35:15.880 line:80%
and was sent off for forced labor.

00:35:16.370 --> 00:35:17.290 line:80%
After that,

00:35:18.060 --> 00:35:19.930 line:80%
Scholar Song helped out.

00:35:21.540 --> 00:35:24.450 line:80%
You see, Kang Dan turned 18 this year.

00:35:24.660 --> 00:35:26.500 line:80%
He's timid and simple-minded.

00:35:27.290 --> 00:35:28.220 line:80%
I just hope

00:35:28.220 --> 00:35:30.140 line:80%
that my younger grandson, Xiaohu,

00:35:30.140 --> 00:35:33.250 line:80%
could be smarter and sharper
than his older brother.

00:35:35.370 --> 00:35:36.180 line:80%
You know,

00:35:36.970 --> 00:35:38.620 line:80%
by the end of the year,

00:35:38.770 --> 00:35:42.430 line:80%
isn't life really just about
having something to look forward to?

00:35:47.450 --> 00:35:49.620 line:80%
Next year, or the year after—

00:35:49.970 --> 00:35:50.810 line:80%
perhaps

00:35:51.410 --> 00:35:52.740 line:80%
things will get better.

00:36:03.850 --> 00:36:04.510 line:80%
Please sit.

00:36:10.580 --> 00:36:12.180 line:80%
What do you want me to write?

00:36:15.300 --> 00:36:17.540 line:80%
Just no more wars,

00:36:18.220 --> 00:36:19.660 line:80%
so that our Kang family

00:36:19.890 --> 00:36:21.290 line:80%
could continue our line.

00:36:23.370 --> 00:36:24.900 line:80%
And I hope my two grandsons,

00:36:25.850 --> 00:36:28.050 line:80%
without their parents to protect them,

00:36:28.410 --> 00:36:30.340 line:80%
could still grow up safe and sound.

00:36:40.060 --> 00:36:40.700 line:80%
Okay.

00:36:50.590 --> 00:36:51.590 line:80%
[Composed]

00:37:08.190 --> 00:37:11.870 line:80%
[Ornamented Beauty]

00:37:16.370 --> 00:37:17.620 line:80%
Greetings, Mother.

00:37:18.950 --> 00:37:20.660 line:80%
May I ask why

00:37:20.770 --> 00:37:22.430 line:80%
you summoned me here, Mother?

00:37:25.770 --> 00:37:28.370 line:80%
It's New Year's Eve,
a time for family reunion.

00:37:28.450 --> 00:37:30.380 line:80%
Do I really need a reason

00:37:30.500 --> 00:37:32.140 line:80%
just to see you?

00:37:33.370 --> 00:37:34.770 line:80%
That's not what I meant.

00:37:41.890 --> 00:37:45.020 line:80%
I wish you a prosperous New Year, Mother.

00:37:45.180 --> 00:37:47.700 line:80%
May peace and health be with you always.

00:37:52.660 --> 00:37:55.720 line:80%
You were betrothed to
the Marquis of Wu'an since birth.

00:37:55.890 --> 00:37:58.220 line:80%
Back when the Marquis of Wu'an
was still around,

00:37:58.220 --> 00:38:00.850 line:80%
he was a heroic young man
with great military merits.

00:38:00.850 --> 00:38:03.710 line:80%
Such a fine man would have been
a great match for you,

00:38:04.100 --> 00:38:06.700 line:80%
yet you said you only saw him
as an older brother

00:38:06.700 --> 00:38:09.300 line:80%
and refused to take him as
your Prince Consort.

00:38:09.810 --> 00:38:11.930 line:80%
And now, this failed scheme

00:38:12.160 --> 00:38:13.540 line:80%
has consumed you.

00:38:15.500 --> 00:38:17.300 line:80%
What do you mean by that, Mother?

00:38:17.450 --> 00:38:19.330 line:80%
Ever since you returned to the palace,

00:38:19.330 --> 00:38:22.660 line:80%
you've used illness as an excuse
multiple times to put off meeting Li Huai'an.

00:38:22.660 --> 00:38:24.410 line:80%
I have already made arrangements.

00:38:24.410 --> 00:38:27.850 line:80%
You will go to the Lantern Festival
with him on the fifteenth.

00:38:28.890 --> 00:38:29.890 line:80%
Mother!

00:38:31.080 --> 00:38:34.970 line:80%
The Gongsun family has been barred from
holding office in the court for generations.

00:38:34.970 --> 00:38:36.370 line:80%
This is an imperial regulation

00:38:36.370 --> 00:38:37.770 line:80%
and must never be defied.

00:38:37.770 --> 00:38:39.030 line:80%
As the Princess Royal,

00:38:39.180 --> 00:38:40.820 line:80%
you must not let that scheme

00:38:40.930 --> 00:38:43.390 line:80%
ruin the grand cause of
our imperial family.

00:38:46.890 --> 00:38:48.740 line:80%
I'm not your pawn, Mother.

00:38:49.270 --> 00:38:52.060 line:80%
And I refuse to be manipulated
in this palace scheme.

00:38:52.060 --> 00:38:54.140 line:80%
You only care about family glory

00:38:54.140 --> 00:38:55.290 line:80%
and imperial regulations, Mother.

00:38:55.290 --> 00:38:58.350 line:80%
Have you ever truly cared about
my happiness or sorrow?

00:38:59.100 --> 00:39:00.300 line:80%
In short, from now on,

00:39:00.500 --> 00:39:03.500 line:80%
you must not see anyone
from the Gongsun family again.

00:39:04.450 --> 00:39:06.110 line:80%
Just cut that thought off now.

00:39:10.500 --> 00:39:12.360 line:80%
If there's nothing else, Mother,

00:39:12.620 --> 00:39:13.890 line:80%
I shall take my leave.

00:39:16.970 --> 00:39:17.930 line:80%
Shu!

00:39:18.890 --> 00:39:20.450 line:80%
Your Highness, where are you going?

00:39:18.980 --> 00:39:21.810 line:80%
[Ornamented Beauty]

00:39:22.060 --> 00:39:23.460 line:80%
I'm going to hang myself.

00:39:23.500 --> 00:39:25.100 line:80%
Do you want to join me, Nanny?

00:39:27.720 --> 00:39:31.090 line:80%
[Composed]

00:39:35.810 --> 00:39:39.450 line:80%
Though loved for its clever words,

00:39:41.410 --> 00:39:45.060 line:80%
the bird yearns to fly free.

00:40:00.180 --> 00:40:01.660 line:80%
Come on.

00:40:02.580 --> 00:40:03.660 line:80%
Let's eat.

00:40:03.660 --> 00:40:04.690 line:80%
It smells so good.

00:40:04.710 --> 00:40:05.580 line:80%
Smells so good.

00:40:05.580 --> 00:40:06.970 line:80%
Thank you. Thank you.

00:40:07.540 --> 00:40:08.540 line:80%
Here.

00:40:09.410 --> 00:40:10.100 line:80%
Yummy, yummy.

00:40:10.100 --> 00:40:10.740 line:80%
Yummy.

00:40:11.990 --> 00:40:12.450 line:80%
Eat up.

00:40:12.450 --> 00:40:13.180 line:80%
It's so good.

00:40:13.500 --> 00:40:14.510 line:80%
Coming up.

00:40:17.030 --> 00:40:19.180 line:80%
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

00:40:33.370 --> 00:40:34.330 line:80%
Let's have another cup.

00:40:34.330 --> 00:40:35.060 line:80%
Fill it up.

00:40:35.410 --> 00:40:36.140 line:80%
Fill it up.

00:40:37.020 --> 00:40:37.880 line:80%
I want some too.

00:40:38.740 --> 00:40:40.850 line:80%
No, you're still injured.

00:40:41.540 --> 00:40:43.200 line:80%
This light liquor won't hurt.

00:40:43.370 --> 00:40:44.410 line:80%
Have some tea instead.

00:40:44.410 --> 00:40:45.450 line:80%
The doctor said

00:40:45.450 --> 00:40:47.290 line:80%
no alcohol until you recover.

00:40:47.580 --> 00:40:48.940 line:80%
I want some too.

00:40:49.620 --> 00:40:51.290 line:80%
Changning, you can't drink either.

00:40:51.290 --> 00:40:53.370 line:80%
Come on, have tea with Zheng.

00:40:59.290 --> 00:41:01.620 line:80%
Eat and drink well. Peace year after year.

00:41:01.620 --> 00:41:02.970 line:80%
Cheers.

00:41:03.330 --> 00:41:04.180 line:80%
Come on.

00:41:16.500 --> 00:41:17.320 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:41:19.290 --> 00:41:20.370 line:80%
Why don't we...

00:41:23.060 --> 00:41:24.330 line:80%
Fireworks!

00:41:29.240 --> 00:41:30.180 line:80%
Let's go watch the fireworks.

00:41:30.180 --> 00:41:32.310 line:80%
Come on, let's go watch the fireworks.

00:41:35.580 --> 00:41:36.910 line:80%
Be careful, Changning.

00:41:38.100 --> 00:41:38.960 line:80%
What did you just say?

00:41:38.960 --> 00:41:40.090 line:80%
I didn't catch that.

00:41:46.450 --> 00:41:48.310 line:80%
I... I said I wanted to drink more.

00:41:51.630 --> 00:41:54.890 line:80%
-Come on, let's go upstairs.
-Let's go upstairs and watch.

00:41:55.450 --> 00:41:56.100 line:80%
Good wine.

00:41:56.770 --> 00:41:57.970 line:80%
Don't drink too much.

00:41:58.330 --> 00:41:59.620 line:80%
I'm perfectly sober.

00:41:59.620 --> 00:42:01.280 line:80%
This wine isn't strong at all.

00:42:04.020 --> 00:42:05.280 line:80%
I'll pour you some tea.

00:42:06.250 --> 00:42:07.510 line:80%
Sober up with some tea.

00:42:15.500 --> 00:42:16.940 line:80%
Looking down on me, huh?

00:42:20.850 --> 00:42:22.540 line:80%
My father can drink
a whole jar of strong liquor,

00:42:22.540 --> 00:42:24.400 line:80%
so I can handle at least half a jar.

00:42:36.450 --> 00:42:38.060 line:80%
This wine isn't intoxicating at all.

00:42:38.060 --> 00:42:39.740 line:80%
Come on, bottoms up.

00:42:41.810 --> 00:42:42.370 line:80%
Come on.

00:42:48.250 --> 00:42:49.770 line:80%
You really are drunk.

00:42:52.220 --> 00:42:53.890 line:80%
I'm totally fine.

00:42:56.060 --> 00:42:57.290 line:80%
Happy New Year.

00:42:57.770 --> 00:42:58.850 line:80%
Happy New Year.

00:43:13.020 --> 00:43:14.930 line:80%
You won't get a baby

00:43:15.410 --> 00:43:17.170 line:80%
without feeding the wolf.

00:43:19.580 --> 00:43:20.330 line:80%
What baby?